701096f-a.title: Bronx: Freeman Street - Boone Avenue
701096f-a.text:
Freeman Street, north side, east from Boone to Westchester Avenues. Shown too is the bridge that carries the Interborough subway across the Bronx River; it is on Westchester Avenue.
August 21, 1940
P. L. Sperr
